        <h1>Join Group Therapy Sessions</h1>
        <p>Group therapy provides a supportive environment where individuals can share their experiences, learn from others, and develop coping strategies together. At MentalMed, we offer various group therapy sessions tailored to different needs and interests.</p>

        <h3>Benefits of Group Therapy</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Supportive Community:</strong> Connect with others who understand what you're going through.</li>
            <li><strong>Shared Experiences:</strong> Learn from the experiences and insights of group members.</li>
            <li><strong>Cost-Effective:</strong> Group sessions are often more affordable than individual therapy.</li>
            <li><strong>Enhanced Communication Skills:</strong> Practice expressing your thoughts and feelings in a safe setting.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Available Group Therapy Sessions</h3>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h4>Anxiety Management</h4>
                <p>Learn effective techniques to manage and reduce anxiety symptoms.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h4>Depression Support</h4>
                <p>Find support and strategies to cope with depression and improve your mood.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h4>Stress Relief</h4>
                <p>Explore methods to alleviate stress and enhance your resilience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h4>Mindfulness and Meditation</h4>
                <p>Practice mindfulness and meditation techniques to increase present-moment awareness.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3>How to Join</h3>
        <p>Joining a group therapy session is easy. Follow these steps:</p>
        <ol>
            <li><a href="/login">Log in</a> to your MentalMed account.</li>
            <li>Navigate to the <a href="/group_therapy">Group Therapy</a> section.</li>
            <li>Select the session that best fits your needs.</li>
            <li>Click on "Join Session" and follow the prompts to confirm your participation.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>If you don't have an account, <a href="/register">register here</a> to get started.</p>
